{"data":{"article":{"html":"<p>After forgetting your password you have two possibilities:</p>\n<h3>1. You still have access to the account</h3>\n<p>This could be the case if you have forgot your password but are still logged in on another device.</p>\n<p>In this case, simply go to <a href=\"https://example.com/settings/security/password/\">https://example.com/settings/security/password/</a> and reset your password.</p>\n<h3>2. You still have access to the mail address</h3>\n<p>In this case, please visit <a href=\"https://example.com/login\">https://example.com/login</a> and click <code>Reset Password</code>.</p>\n<h3>3. You don't have access to the mail address</h3>\n<p>In this case please <a href=\"https://example.com/support\">contact out support team</a>. We will try to verify that it is you and reset your password for you.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"account/forgot-password","title":"I forgot my password"}},"footer":{"html":"<div \n  align=\"center\" \n  style=\"display:flex; justify-content: center;align-items:center;flex-direction:column;margin-top:2.5rem;\">\n  <h4>Still have questions?</h4>\n  <a href=\"https://example.com/support\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\"\n      stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"feather feather-send\">\n      <line x1=\"22\" y1=\"2\" x2=\"11\" y2=\"13\"></line>\n      <polygon points=\"22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2\"></polygon>\n    </svg> \n    <span style=\"margin-left: 0.2rem;\">Send us a message</span>\n  </a>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;\">\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"feather feather-info\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=